+
+           A new algorithm for calculating the difference, intersection,
+           exclusive-or or union of arbitrary polygon sets.
+
+File:      gpc.c
+Author:    Alan Murta (email: gpc@cs.man.ac.uk)
+Version:   2.32
+Date:      17th December 2004
